xTranslate
==========
xTranslate is an open source tool for translate selected text.

Translate selected text an any application using google translate and pop up result whith notify-send.
In addition, plays mp3 from google translate by mp123.

Alt+4 translate from ru to en
Alt+5 translate from en to ru

Install:
sudo apt-get install python
sudo apt-get install mpg123

Copy .xbindkeysrc to home dir
Copy to /usr/bin 
	translate.py
	translate.sh
Copy ico.jpg to
	/usr/local/share/ico.jpg

Requirements:
	notify-send
	python
	mpg123

Tested on ubuntu 3.0.0-15-generic x86_64
